  <summary date="2021-08-24T14:34:55Z" status="Introduced in House">Recognizing the Role of Direct Support Professionals Act 

This bill requires the Office of Management and Budget to establish a separate category within the Standard Occupational Classification system for direct support professionals (i.e., individuals who provide services to promote independence in individuals with a disability) for data reporting purposes.</summary>
